cobbler recepies do you have any cobbler recipies you want to share i'm always looking for original and unique recipies thanks these are my favorite cobbler recipes berry cobbler ingredients tablespoons butter cup all purpose flour cup sugar teaspoon baking powder teaspoon salt cup milk cups of sliced fresh peaches or nectarines or whole blueberries strawberries raspberries blackberries or a combination of fruits or a ounce package of frozen berries tablespoon sugar directions adjust oven rack to upper middle position and heat oven to degrees put butter in an inch square or inch round pan set in oven to melt when butter has melted remove pan from oven whisk flour cup of sugar baking powder and salt in small bowl add milk whisk to form a smooth batter pour batter into pan then scatter fruit over batter sprinkle with remaining tb of sugar bake until batter browns and fruit bubbles to minutes serve warm or at room temperature with a dollop of whipped cream or a small scoop of vanilla ice cream if desired peach raspberry cobbler ingredients cups sliced fresh peaches cup fresh raspberries cup sugar teaspoon ground cinnamon tablespoon fresh lemon juice cup butter cups all purpose flour tablespoons baking powder teaspoon salt cup sugar cup milk directions in a bowl mix the peaches raspberries cup sugar cinnamon and lemon juice allow to sit while proceeding with remaining steps preheat oven to degrees f degrees c melt the butter in a x inch glass baking dish in the preheating oven and evenly coat dish remove from heat in a bowl mix the flour baking powder salt and cup sugar mix in milk just until dry ingredients are evenly moist pour evenly into the buttered baking dish scoop peach and raspberry mixture over the batter bake minutes in the preheated oven until golden brown Cuisine of the Philippines Idli Tofu Vinegar Bacon Bagel Barbecue Cookie French toast Milkshake Cooking weights and measures Haggis Baklava German cuisine Chili con carne Cuisine of Brazil Muesli Breakfast